Get ready for a new year peeps. Have a blast 2017. *warning* the next few paragraphs are unimportant as it is only a few notes for myself.

2016.. well.. Some part of it was really a blast. Met some new awesome friends, experience something new, tried to challenge some of my limits. Spent some great times with those whom i hold most dear. Got some box checked on the bucket-list. I grew.
On the other hand, i lost my way and still have. Spending half of the year trying to understand seemingly superficial things, yet important for me. One thing i learned, it's not a problem getting lost, because it always felt good finding your way back again. Heck, i don't even know what the problems are. 
Notes for 2017 for myself in case i desperately desperate for a fresh air and need to re-align my thinking in the next 12 months. ‚Ä¢enjoy getting lost ‚Ä¢stop self pitying ‚Ä¢be proud ‚Ä¢enjoy being with yourself.
‚Ä¢set goals, try your best to achieve them, don't fret if you fail. ‚Ä¢troubles are waves, ride them ‚Ä¢change your poisonous daily habits.
‚Ä¢pray,love,live, shoot, eat, read, learn, travel

See you in 365 days, cheers, Godspeed for those who reads. Oh. On a side note, this marks the 365 photo challenge i set for myself. Enjoys.
